---
import { LinkButton } from "@astrojs/starlight/components";

interface TaxonomyItem {
  title: string;
  description: string;
  note: string;
  href: string;
}

interface LandscapeRow {
  name: string;
  href: string;
  intro: string;
  category: string;
  runtimeForm: string;
  starsBadge?: string;
}

interface Props {
  taxonomy: TaxonomyItem[];
  rows: LandscapeRow[];
}

const { taxonomy, rows } = Astro.props;
---

<section id="ecosystem" class="overview-section">
  <div class="overview-section-head">
    <div class="overview-prose">
      <p class="section-label">生态与比较</p>
      <h2>现在有哪些代表性选择，以及这些项目应该怎么放在一起比较？</h2>
      <p>
        最大的误区不是漏看项目，而是把不在同一层的问题拿来做同一种比较。
      </p>
      <p>
        更稳的读法是先分对象层和实践层，再判断它落在宿主、agent harness，还是更大的任务编排层。
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="ecosystem-actions not-content">
      <LinkButton href="/everything-harness-engineering/ecosystem-comparison/" variant="minimal" icon="right-arrow">
        进入生态与比较
      </LinkButton>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="ecosystem-kinds not-content">
    <p>比较时先把对象归类和实践定位分开，再看下面四种常见位置：</p>
    <ul class="ecosystem-kind-list">
      {taxonomy.map((item) => (
        <li>
          <strong>{item.title.replace(/^\d+\.\s*/, "")}</strong>
          <span>{item.note.replace(/^典型问题：/, "")}</span>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>
  </div>

  <p class="ecosystem-preview-note">
    下面这张表先把主要项目放到同一张比较坐标里；其中有些格子写的是对象归类，有些写的是实践定位。
  </p>

  <div class="table-wrap not-content">
    <table class="landscape-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>套件</th>
          <th>简介</th>
          <th>定位</th>
          <th>运行形态</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        {rows.map((row) => (
          <tr>
            <td>
              <div class="suite-cell">
                <a href={row.href}>{row.name}</a>
                {row.starsBadge && (
                  <img
                    src={row.starsBadge}
                    alt={`${row.name} GitHub stars`}
                    class="stars-badge"
                    loading="lazy"
                  />
                )}
              </div>
            </td>
            <td>{row.intro}</td>
            <td>{row.category}</td>
            <td>{row.runtimeForm}</td>
          </tr>
        ))}
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</section>
